		<RichText x="56" y="434" fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="449" height="30" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffffff">Gleaming Charge: Frostnight Scion</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ff99ff" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣利用巨尾进行至多2段的横扫攻击，均造成<span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣操控巨尾，施放3个明雷珠，随后变为闪电袭击前方，均造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，中央的雷珠会尝试袭击玩家；该技能仅在「晦隐」状态下施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="398" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣抬起前身向前跺下，造成<span color="#ffacff">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="407" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣将尾部掷向地面，造成<span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害，同时产生一道落雷，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害；「晦隐」状态下落雷增加至3道。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣转身翻越，进入「<span textDecoration="underline">晦隐</span><span>」状态，该状态下灵嗣施放技能前后都会闪现，并且全抗提升，解除对</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素</span><span>的免疫。<br/>不处于「晦隐」状态下持续附着</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="398" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣抬起前身向前跺下，造成<span color="#ffacff">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
