		<RichText x="14" y="941" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="18" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="36" height="44" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="18" color="#ffffff">深渊<br/>晦隐</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="998" width="433" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">晦隐：抗打断0，全抗性提升<span color="#ffccbf">60%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffccbf">120%</span><span>，允许受到雷元素伤害；充能条总量</span><span color="#ffacff">100</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">150</span><span>(深渊)，受到</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素</span><span>攻击后根据雷元素的量积攒</span><span color="#ffacff">20n</span><span>或</span><span color="#ffacff">3</span><span>，受到月反应伤害积攒</span><span color="#ffacff">3</span><span>，充满退出状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
